# User Config — Template

Copy this file to `user-config.md` (gitignored) and fill in your details.
Agents read this file at startup to parameterize task IDs and output paths.

---

username_prefix: yourname          # used in task IDs (e.g. yourname-20260303-my-task) and direct-output/ paths
full_name: Your Name
email: your.name@teampicnic.com
team: Your Team / Domain
